=<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Conectar WhatsApp — Mútua Digital</title>
  <style>
    :root{
      --mutua-1:#FF9B00;
      --mutua-2:#FF8300;
      --mutua-3:#FF7000;
      --mutua-4:#FF5500;
      --mutua-5:#FF4F42;
      --mutua-6:#F23E25;
      --gray-1:#666666;
      --gray-2:#C4C4C4;
      --bg:#fafafa;
      --card:#ffffff;
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial;
      background: radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 10% -10%, rgba(255,155,0,.20), transparent 55%),
                  radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 90% -10%, rgba(242,62,37,.16), transparent 55%),
                  var(--bg);
      color:var(--gray-1);
    }
    header{
      padding:24px 16px 8px;
      display:flex;
      justify-content:center;
    }
    .wrap{
      max-width: 980px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 8px 16px 28px;
    }
    .topbar{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:14px;
      padding:14px 16px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,155,0,.10), rgba(242,62,37,.08));
      border: 1px solid rgba(196,196,196,.55);
    }
    .logo{
      width:160px;
      height:auto;
      display:block;
    }
    .title{
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      gap:2px;
      line-height:1.2;
    }
    .title h1{
      margin:0;
      font-size:18px;
      color:#333;
      font-weight:700;
    }
    .title p{
      margin:0;
      font-size:13px;
      opacity:.9;
    }
    .grid{
      margin-top:14px;
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr .9fr;
      gap:14px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 860px){
      .grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .logo{width:140px}
    }
    .card{
      background:var(--card);
      border:1px solid rgba(196,196,196,.55);
      border-radius:18px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.05);
      padding:16px;
    }
    .badge{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:8px;
      padding:6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,155,0,.18), rgba(242,62,37,.14));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,155,0,.25);
      font-size:12px;
      color:#333;
      font-weight:600;
    }
    ol{
      margin:12px 0 0 18px;
      padding:0;
    }
    li{
      margin:10px 0;
      font-size:14px;
      line-height:1.45;
    }
    .hint{
      margin-top:12px;
      padding:12px;
      border-radius:14px;
      border:1px dashed rgba(196,196,196,.75);
      background: rgba(196,196,196,.08);
      font-size:13px;
    }
    .qrbox{
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      gap:10px;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
    }
    .qr{
      width: 320px;
      max-width: 100%;
      background:#fff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(196,196,196,.65);
      padding:14px;
    }
    .actions{
      display:flex;
      gap:10px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      justify-content:center;
      margin-top:6px;
    }
    .btn{
      appearance:none;
      border:0;
      cursor:pointer;
      padding:10px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight:700;
      font-size:13px;
      color:#222;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,155,0,.90), rgba(242,62,37,.88));
    }
    .btn.secondary{
      background: transparent;
      border:1px solid rgba(196,196,196,.9);
      color:#333;
      font-weight:700;
    }
    .footer{
      margin-top:12px;
      font-size:12px;
      opacity:.85;
      text-align:center;
    }
    code{background: rgba(196,196,196,.18); padding:2px 6px; border-radius:8px}
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <div class="wrap" style="width:100%">
      <div class="topbar">
        <!-- Troque o src para o seu logo público (recomendado) -->
        <img class="logo" src="https://mutua.digital/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/mutua-digital-logo.svg" alt="Mútua Digital" />
        <div class="title">
          <h1>Conectar WhatsApp ao Atendimento Automatizado: MAC Transporte Executivo</h1>
          <p>Escaneie o QR Code abaixo no WhatsApp Business para concluir a conexão com segurança.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid">
        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Instruções rápidas</span>
          <ol>
            <li>No celular, abra o <b>WhatsApp Business</b>.</li>
            <li>Vá em <b>Configurações</b> → <b>Aparelhos conectados</b>.</li>
            <li>Toque em <b>Conectar um aparelho</b>.</li>
            <li>Aponte a câmera para o QR Code desta página.</li>
            <li>Se o QR expirar, clique em <b>Atualizar QR</b>.</li>
          </ol>

          <div class="hint">
            <b>Dicas:</b> mantenha o celular com internet durante a conexão. Se aparecer “QR inválido”, atualize a página.
            Em alguns casos o WhatsApp exige desbloqueio por biometria/senha antes de escanear.
          </div>
        </section>

        <aside class="card qrbox">
          <span class="badge">Seu QR Code</span>

          <div class="qr">
            <img
              src="data:image/png;base64,{{ $json.base64 }}"
              alt="QR Code de conexão do WhatsApp"
              style="width:100%; height:auto; display:block;"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="actions">
            <button class="btn" onclick="location.reload()">Atualizar QR</button>
            <button class="btn secondary" onclick="window.print()">Imprimir / Salvar PDF</button>
          </div>

          <div class="footer">
            Suporte Mútua Digital • Se necessário, envie um print desta tela para sua equipe.
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>
</body>
</html>

